name: UNOS_CLIN_INFO_3
description: Additional information reported to the United Network for Organ Sharing (UNOS) for each of the registry records or forms.

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the registry data record.

columns.name: DNR_VIR_TESTED_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor was tested for HIV, CMV, HBV, HCV or EBV prior to the donation.

columns.name: VIR_CMV_TESTED_YN
columns.description: Indicates the presence of CMV.

columns.name: VIR_CMV_DISEASE_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any CMV related clinical disease.

columns.name: VIR_CMV_NUC_ACID_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's CMV nucleic acid test results.

columns.name: VIR_CMV_CULTURE_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's CMV culture test results.

columns.name: VIR_CMV_PREUNET_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's pre-UNet CMV data.

columns.name: VIR_HIV_TESTED_YN
columns.description: Indicates the presence of any of several retroviruses indicative of AIDS.

columns.name: VIR_HIV_SCREEN_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HIV screening test results.

columns.name: VIR_HIV_CONFIRM_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HIV confirmation test results.

columns.name: VIR_HIV_DISEASE_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any HIV related clinical disease.

columns.name: VIR_HIV_ANTIB_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HIV antibody test results.

columns.name: VIR_HIV_RNA_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HIV RNA test results.

columns.name: VIR_HBV_TESTED_YN
columns.description: Indicates the presence of HBV or serum hepatitis.

columns.name: VIR_HBV_DISEASE_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any HBV related clinical disease.

columns.name: VIR_HBV_LVR_HISTO_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HBV liver histology test results.

columns.name: VIR_HBV_DNA_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HBV DNA test results.

columns.name: VIR_HBV_HDV_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HBV HDV (Delta virus) test results.

columns.name: VIR_HCV_TESTED_YN
columns.description: Indicates the presence of HCV.

columns.name: VIR_HCV_DISEASE_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any HCV related clinical disease.

columns.name: VIR_HCV_LVR_HISTO_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HCV liver histology test results.

columns.name: VIR_HCV_ANTIB_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HCV antibody test results.

columns.name: VIR_HCV_RIBA_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HCV RIBA test results.

columns.name: VIR_HCV_RNA_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's HCV RNA test results.

columns.name: VIR_EBV_TESTED_YN
columns.description: Indicates the presence of EBV or EB virus.

columns.name: VIR_EBV_DISEASE_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient had any EBV related clinical disease.

columns.name: VIR_EBV_IGG_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's EBV IgG test results.

columns.name: VIR_EBV_IGM_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's EBV IgM test results.

columns.name: VIR_EBV_DNA_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's EBV DNA test results.

columns.name: UNOS_CANCER_HX_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor had a history of cancer prior to the donation.

columns.name: UNOS_CANCER_HX_SP
columns.description: The name of the cancer of which the donor had a history prior to the donation.

columns.name: CANCER_FREE_INTERVL
columns.description: If the donor had a history of cancer, the number of years the donor was cancer-free prior to donation.

columns.name: CANCER_FREE_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: Specifies the reason why the number of years the donor was free of the cancer is not available.

columns.name: UNOS_HX_HYPERTNSN_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor had a history of hypertension prior to donation.

columns.name: UNOS_HX_HYPT_DIET_C_NAME
columns.description: If the donor had a history of hypertension, indicates whether diet was used as a treatment method.

columns.name: UNOS_HX_HYPT_DIUR_C_NAME
columns.description: If the donor had a history of hypertension, indicates whether diuretics were used as a treatment method.

columns.name: UNOS_HX_HYPT_MED_C_NAME
columns.description: If the donor had a history of hypertension, indicates whether medication was used as a treatment method.

columns.name: PREOP_BP_SYSTOLIC
columns.description: The living donor's systolic blood pressure prior to donation.

columns.name: PREOP_BP_SYST_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: Specifies why the living donor's systolic blood pressure prior to donation is not available.

columns.name: PREOP_BP_DIASTOLIC
columns.description: The living donor's diastolic blood pressure prior to donation.

columns.name: PREOP_BP_DIAS_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: Specifies why the living donor's diastolic blood pressure prior to donation is not available.

columns.name: PREOP_URINE_RATIO
columns.description: The donor's urinalysis protein-creatinine ratio prior to donation.

columns.name: PREOP_URINE_PRTN_C_NAME
columns.description: The living donor's urinalysis urine protein prior to donation.

columns.name: UNOS_KI_GLOMERO_C_NAME
columns.description: The living donor's glomerulosclerosis if the living donor had a kidney biopsy prior to donation.

columns.name: UNOS_KI_PROC_TYPE_C_NAME
columns.description: The kidney intended procedure type.

columns.name: CNV_LAPAROS_OPEN_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether there was a conversion from laparoscopic to open procedure if laparoscopic was selected for intended procedure type.

columns.name: CIGARETTE_HX_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor has a history of cigarette use.

columns.name: UNOS_CGR_PCK_YR_C_NAME
columns.description: The number of packs of cigarettes the donor smoked per day multiplied by the number of years if the donor has a history of cigarette use.

columns.name: UNOS_ABSTINENCE_C_NAME
columns.description: The number of months the donor has abstained from cigarettes if the donor has a history of cigarette use.

columns.name: UNOS_OTH_TOBACCO_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor has a history of other tobacco use.

columns.name: UNOS_DNR_DEATH_C_NAME
columns.description: The cause of death if the living donor died.
entries: Domino Liver Donor Transplant Related Death (Liver donors only)

columns.name: NONAUTOLOG_BLOOD_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether non-autologous blood was administered to the donor.

columns.name: PRBC_UNIT_NUM
columns.description: The number of units the donor received for PRBC if non-autologous blood was administered to the donor.

columns.name: PLATELETS_UNIT_NUM
columns.description: The number of units the donor received for platelets if non-autologous blood was administered to the donor.

columns.name: FFP_UNIT_NUM
columns.description: The number of units the donor received for FFP if non-autologous blood was administered to the donor.

columns.name: KI_VSC_COMP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor experienced vascular complications requiring intervention during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_VSC_COMP_OTH
columns.description: Free text description of the kidney vascular complication(s) if the donor experienced vascular complications requiring intervention during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_OTH_COMP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor experienced other complication requiring intervention during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_OTH_COMP_SP
columns.description: Free text description of the kidney other complication(s) if the donor experienced vascular complications requiring intervention during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_REOP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor required reoperation the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_REOP_BLEEDING_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether bleeding is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_BLEEDING_DT
columns.description: The reoperation date if bleeding is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_HERN_REP_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether hernia repair is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_HERN_REP_DT
columns.description: The reoperation date if hernia repair is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_BOW_OBST_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether bowel obstruction is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_BOW_OBST_DT
columns.description: The reoperation date if bowel obstruction is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_VSC_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether vascular is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_VSC_DT
columns.description: The reoperation date if vascular is the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_OTH_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether there is a specific reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_OTH_SP
columns.description: Free text description of the reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: KI_REOP_OTH_DT
columns.description: The reoperation date if there is a specific reason for reoperation during first six weeks.

columns.name: READMISSION_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor required any readmission after the initial discharge during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: READMISSION_SP
columns.description: Free text description of the reason why the donor required readmission after the initial discharge during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: READMISSION_DT
columns.description: The date of the first readmission.

columns.name: KI_OTH_PROC_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor required other interventional procedures after the initial discharge during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_OTH_PROC_SP
columns.description: Free text description of the procedure(s) if the donor required other interventional procedures after the initial discharge during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: KI_OTH_PROC_DT
columns.description: The date of procedure if the donor required other interventional procedures after the initial discharge during the first 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: POSTOP_BP_SYSTOLIC
columns.description: The donor's systolic blood pressure within 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: POSTOP_BP_SYST_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: The reason why the donor's systolic blood pressure is not available.

columns.name: POSTOP_BP_DIASTOLIC
columns.description: The donor's diastolic blood pressure within 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: POSTOP_BP_DIAS_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: The reason why the donor's diastolic blood pressure is not available.

columns.name: POSTOP_URINE_RATIO
columns.description: The donor's urinalysis protein-creatinine ratio within 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: POSTOP_URINE_PRTN_C_NAME
columns.description: The donor's urinalysis urine protein within 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: DNR_HYPERTNSN_MED_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether donor developed hypertension requiring medication within 6 weeks after the donation.

columns.name: ORGAN_RECOVERY_DT
columns.description: Date of donor organ recovery.

columns.name: UNOS_CATSCAN_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether a CAT scan was performed for the patient.

columns.name: UNOS_CATSCAN_SP
columns.description: The patient's CAT scan result.

columns.name: UNOS_MRI_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether an MRI was performed for the patient.

columns.name: UNOS_MRI_SP
columns.description: The patient's MRI result.

columns.name: UNOS_ULTRASND_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether an ultrasound was performed for the patient.

columns.name: UNOS_ULTRASND_SP
columns.description: The patient's ultrasound result.

columns.name: READMISSION_DT_ST_C_NAME
columns.description: The reason why the first readmission date is not available.

columns.name: KI_COMP_C_NAME
columns.description: Indicates whether the donor experienced kidney complications.

columns.name: KI_COMP_SP
columns.description: Free text description of the type of kidney complications.

columns.name: UNOS_DNR_DEATH_SP
columns.description: Free text description of the cause of death if the living donor died.

columns.name: UNOS_RECOVR_ORG_C_NAME
columns.description: The organ recovered from the donor that is being addressed by this form.
